# Data Cleaning: 

```{r}
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
#Reading in the data set 
#Filtering out NA values in all columns
#Dropping unwanted columns (Trt1 & tr2)
#Removing any sows that were induced
Data <- ST_project[,-14]
Data <- Data[,-14]%>%
  drop_na(TNB,SB,SB_perc)%>%
  filter(., Induce == "0")
```
